## 💡 Example Walkthrough

```cpp
n = 28

low = 1, high = 28

mid = 14 → 14² = 196 > 28 → move left
mid = 7  → 49 > 28 → move left
mid = 3  → 9 ≤ 28 → move right
mid = 5  → 25 ≤ 28 → move right
mid = 6  → 36 > 28 → move left

Final answer = 5
```

